$ Oracle: Lateral inline views

A → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/select/subquery can be marked with the `lateral` keyword which turns it into a *lateral inline view*.

Lateral inline views were introduces with Oracle 12c.

gh|Oracle-Patterns|/SQL/select/12c/lateral.sql||

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/join/apply/cross[`cross apply`]
